activities.description: Wrestling match begins with Leroy Green, Cashflow, and Matt Travis in the ring.
Cashflow executes a move on Leroy Green, disobeying the referee's orders.
Cashflow prepares to attack Leroy Green, Matt Travis is ready to intervene.
Joe Gacy enters the ring and attacks Cashflow.
Joe Gacy performs a springboard double stunner on Cashflow.
Leroy Green performs a guillotine neck breaker on Matt Travis.
Joe Gacy pins Matt Travis for the win.
The referee raises Joe Gacy's hand, declaring him the winner.
